    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved by a single owner. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, having been maintained to the highest standards with all service records available. It represents a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
