    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs like a champ, and has been super well-maintained over the years. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great and feels smooth on the road, this is the one for you! Come swing by and take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
