    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example features a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Maintenance is up to date, including a documented VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. Equipped with Bilstein dampers for sharpened handling, the car delivers precise feedback and linear power delivery. Cosmetically honest with minor patina, it remains a visceral, driver-centric machine ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 34500.0,
