    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2019 Lexus RX 350 that perfectly embodies the blend of reliability and luxury. The Atomic Silver exterior has been well-preserved, retaining a brilliant luster; upon close inspection, you will find only minor road-wear consistent with standard highway use, such as small stone chips on the front bumper. The interior features Parchment leather seating that remains firm and supple, free from any tears or unpleasant odors. All cabin electronics, including the intuitive navigation system, heated seats, and the premium 12-speaker audio system, are in full working order. Under the hood, the 3.5L V6 engine runs smoothly, backed by a consistent service history including a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This vehicle is a solid, dependable choice for anyone seeking a premium driving experience without the premium price tag. It has been cared for diligently and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
